The paper deals with the problem of learning a graph using queries, which is a fundamental problem in machine learning and theoretical computer science. The paper uses techniques from graph theory, information theory, and computational complexity, which are all relevant to the sub-categories of cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
